ons.  Theo, Giancarlo and the rest of the team walked us through all the options, answered every question we had, did impeccable work during installation, and stayed on the project until it was approved by PSE.  They were such great partners in this we are using them for our next set of solar panel installations.  I highly recommend their services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arup Biswas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmjF_colKYbHdbO-nvsBpJ6um9tl4KSd2i_APaxWoS7QrmFsq7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"About a month ago, Northwest Electric and Solar installed a 13 kW solar panel system along with a Tesla Powerwall 3 in our house, and we have been very happy with the experience. Since we have a concrete tile roof, our options were limited—only two installers we found support this roof type. NW Solar had the higher quote, but we chose them because they are a Tesla Premier installer, which made access to the Powerwall 3 easy, and they offered a better warranty than the other installer.\n\nInitially, there was a discrepancy between the original quote and the revised amount, which was a bit disappointing. However, after that, the communication and installation process went very smoothly. Rob, the electrician, and the three other installers arrived promptly at 7 AM on the first day and completed a flawless installation over four days. They handled all permitting and the net meter installation without any issues.\n\nSo far, the panels are performing perfectly, generating about 50% of our electricity consumption in November. The Powerwall 3 also kicked in instantly during a recent power outage, which was very reassuring.\n\nOverall, our experience with NW Solar has been excellent. We highly recommend them to anyone looking to install solar panels and a battery backup system. I will update this review over the years as we continue to use their system.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shane Ruangdet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTlDMtamH-pIzDsdYPapRYZsUrl51yjE1aNFxHCpO8bYS2KKUE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience with Northwest Electric \u0026 Solar! They recently installed my Tesla Wall Connector, and everything about the process was smooth, professional, and efficient. From the start, they offered me the best quote compared to other companies I contacted. Cam, the electrician, was excellent—punctual, knowledgeable, and very courteous. The installation was done cleanly and with great attention to detail. I couldn’t be happier with the outcome. Highly recommend Northwest Electric \u0026 Solar for any EV charger installation or electrical work!\n\nThank you Jeff, Jacob, and Cam!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0eB9C4U2MlL4etwxadtYARru5F_ja7Hs8Ja_IIGt8qvkS-zqTKdsl6mFPop_4Ht-PfTBYizq8Lo4CJ1O7yj_PBsrkseeSvNfB9LR86Uc_XMzR54gdhEf1VpVpcbFQypCt6mIYj=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KNTlo_DVZ-r0yHR59dgIYLUwWNfIhHHWXbZe_87gKJpqWMw2H22y_GOwFywuk_S1OP7iiLib6cOhlrrtYu0igvEJ3g8hIct8xErzXZYC7zldl-jUTCKppZ245WZyv__pnQWPU_w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn34qfns0ev6sKboMwdoe8OvHW7Cn0_1a9pBrFb5orKUYXb7Y2CcAJxRAd9FY-crchX__6rpNRXwLhIAM3RRofxAHqVibZWPAAlDhQd5v7MtGD6w72FF7I5n8nQIhgIpvfTbL6mt=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Dg4XVD2JoCbnvCEZa99IgAi--WTI5B8z6No8Co2-XpNfizpfLD9jF0Atry3NBmIXW0ZIhxkGjdOzOxMmVN3BB8lxZUb15q4isYgElGtuQnXYTi6mixNbAzkDKWnnqDoZcgioaJA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3hJxwnGT43aDez_kCW0KabFlOeD0AGWpuzR12wLpPKpXOxYH8J0BvwMNBibQtBl3_AoFMcO08A4thlANr4u9m27vGbky-0VMmw1ON_oetp8TaDHciN93J_p0vb1qoCYqQpLaXi=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22HMRYTwZJvakVI5eUsnm79QdeUqc7ZIHdgjep5ttlfMoUtAPGDSwwv4SmeCpukwU2o6JIxTd-CqmDVm-JfNx4v-dVUX-jA6mVds2R7CtOBElk5qEUE_z1Q9_1XSa5pQjJ6ggH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qFoioe8bq6G_0EkcsuslnmnxgcF-Dmi3ORmxwmLJqDWuY5