rofilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9oXfyoJcAcvUXdKPqrfj8ktF2QX1vZPhY29c_pilotm12MQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience with NWES!  All aspects of the process were great!  From Jonathon's initial contact, dealing with Cory and Cheryl and the install team.........all went SO smooth and your expertise was apparent.  We thank you and the NWES team very much.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ken He","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaQX3FUibDeKPVQ8PhXKXOqoi7Yy43_C139YwpHvvthMwefPzH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came upon this well reviewed electric vehicle charger installed company by Google search. Communications has been smooth, timely, and excellent. Very easy getting a quote through the online portal. Pricing was extremely competitive and lower than other quotes. Scheduling and install process went smoothly. Finished product looks excellent. Technician was very professional and kept the work area clean. Highly recommend.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn342GYFfyGaaHP4w9DlKugIMJqcoq2N1hNervB1NwYos10KeR5SfqUd1slRIlrgkUsYv5iFWlcrodAtR0pUZ8lkbVxHAD_ufwsO4t9vmim9Y5suRuED8fxMizGA65OtIJxZt3q9=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-31"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
