},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGjPkrppLP1iMXgH4xXYhDmzjVQzlX5F_slOAq6w3-aXVusxETXlErDwp0PfldLYSA_2bPsneTeMF9GFaO4U_tExM5fTdvII97oryeX21k1b0avUojGvUOENnQrCJf6K_6dbscZdw=w298-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://clienthub.getjobber.com/hubs/9bdf84cc-5f51-4a59-9a68-9f3a558f866e/public/requests/4593943/new?rwg_token=AFd1xnHHmc7ajopXdesrAYSItctSKj-aYD_vCEsn4rE4g5XPRO8X-Ai799qEPR8LqObWAVbJcQvQgZjCJ4cdtuRPV6pAXPI72x40AdCv8Cp3pCIZnQWv-_Q%3D","source":"getjobber.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"109455693165110323801","name":"MOGOVOLT (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109455693165110323801"},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Creek","street":"23825 45th Ave SE","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98021","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"James Rooney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ5g15VqyzWsr8NSmu76O7j2YpMI9YW3OSPjIYSdAjUExtMuYv6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had all the knob and tube replaced and power brought to an outside wall for a heat pump. This is the second time we have hired MOGOVOLT and again they did a fantastic job. They were very smart about cutting into the wall to run the new wires and greatly surpassed my expectations. Each night before they left they did a stellar job cleaning up. We got a few quotes for this job and they came in very reasonable, especially over the larger cooperate companies. 10/10 would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicholas Wilkinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMlMucx9PXQotF4m3oZrnwROm3oJyYw7YBdCjzs_i8Ttux6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Mogovolt. I saw one of their vans out doing a project for my neighbor so I gave them a call. The estimate was fast, the work was scheduled without any complexity, and the team showed up right on time.\n\nThe work was done really well, very tidy, very complete. I had several aspects to the overall project — new panel, hot tub circuit, more circuits for water heater and dryer — and I’m really happy with it. They did a very professional job, I asked for a modification to run some wires through joists and it was not a problem. They were friendly and professional, and had a good plan to get the work done and minimize the electricity being off.\n\nThe inspector said they did a very good job and he had seen their work before so wasn’t surprised. It looked good, and they corrected something with the grounding too. I would absolutely recommend Mogovolt and will call them again for my next project!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Faghin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGJANfE-8JyzNnc3zhx3lf_nFoZcZ25Vx9CO2hZPnteIL-eIqr5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Daniel and the whole Mogovolt team were very responsive and communicated extremely well. They installed new pathway lighting and a new electrical box as well as an ev charging station for us. In all aspects of their work they were very efficient and diligent. We would highly recommend them for electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Veatch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXj1ayNtMLga4-T4dW01VwTprZsTkaZVxuzzp2CMVNMncp064=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Mogovolt team were fantastic! They provided a fair quote, did quick (and fastidiously clean) work, and made thoughtful recommendations while onsite performing the work. I would strongly recommend and will be hiring them when I need electrical work done in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theodore Furr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhbH0SDfJ-L7jF0x3XLLaJDfbZvt6BtulOCktZyV3e56XD1XI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Easy to schedule, arrived on time, did great work, easy to coordinate with.  Professional and patient with EV installation and set up.  Answered questions and stayed until confirmed that everything worked properly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanner Lyons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwenO82XHOuB5jyAiMGNKVU3Yzv7js-VV1nsZRHLCL-14GSvc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I could give Mogovolt a 6-star rating, I absolutely would. Before becoming a General Contractor, I spent several years working alongside them as a Project Manager for different company on countless home remodels—and their work consistently speaks for itself.\n\nFor the past six years, they’ve been my go-to electrical team on every single project I’ve managed or been a part of. They’re always punctual, efficient, incredibly hard-working, and their work passes inspection flawlessly every single time.\n\nWhen I started managing my own projects as a GC, I knew I needed an electrical partner who shared my values of honesty, integrity, and uncompromising quality. With Mogovolt, I found exactly that—and I’ve never once looked back.\n\nI would highly recommend Mogovolt for your next project!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amelia Hertog","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUefrd9wbCf8OQsB8q12-yer8IrgVD_fgaSzAP_MiN1HhS6Aqs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve hired Mogovolt Electrical for two new build homes, and Daniel and his team have been exceptional every time. They deliver top-quality electrical work, are trustworthy, professional, and great communicators, and their pricing is fair and transparent.\nIf you’re searching for a reliable residential electrician or electrical contractor near me, look no further. Mogovolt shows up on time, keeps you informed, and gets the job done right the first time. They’re creative, efficient, and easy to work with, which makes every project stress-free.I confidently recommend Mogovolt to all my family, friends, and real estate clients because they consistently provide outstanding service, excellent workmanship, and true peace of mind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kate Koeppel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVze_xhiPvg2v9R7jX7FtwOfmsQYT8wiD7sAthkLYnd5Dysqy8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Mogovolt to replace all knob and tube wiring in our 100 year old home in Queen Anne and update all outlets and switches with new brass hardware. Additionally, we upgraded our overhead service to 200 amps and installed a new larger panel and hardwired all smoke and CO detectors.\n\nI got quotes from a number of local companies, and while all were close in their pricing, Mogovolt’s came in a bit lower, with a number of very strong referrals from neighbors, as well as Homeowner’s Club.\n\nThis project ended up being a more complicated project than we anticipated, because old houses have secrets- ours happened to have a lot more active knob and tube than we had originally anticipated when we bought the house. The Mogovolt team from start to finish was incredibly detailed in their estimates, explanations and ideas for updating our wiring with not just solutions that we liked, but were well-thought through, up to code aligned with new building standards. Communication was outstanding- even when I didn’t understand something they took the time to explain different decisions and possible solutions.\n\nThe team was incredibly polite, tidy and thoughtful in our home. Adi and Ben were always very communicative and gave us great morning and end of day updates- additionally they were happy to talk through solutions and explain, and reexplain more than once a number of tricky decisions we had to think through and understand. The whole team is clearly very experienced, detail-oriented and extremely professional, they kept each of their work areas clean and organized daily. I would not hesitate to hire them again for any electrical work big or small. This was a huge job and put so much effort in from the beginning to end, I really can’t recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
