7pP0=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=RVkcfT5vD_W9n_yBXo2rvA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=355.94904\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101535720146111446571","name":"Konsker Electric (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101535720146111446571"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Wedgwood","street":"2608 NE 82nd St","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98115","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"A.J. Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-fP9moE2z-aFFC2rV4Rcwv5-voJlmRuJfWjlrXJVPswUABJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A couple years ago Robert installed a new main breaker for us and did a great job. So when it was time for us to get a whole home standby generator, he’s the first person I called. Robert and his company are honest, ethical, reasonable and responsible. Our new Generac was installed carefully, correctly and quickly. And I now have the peace of mind I was looking for, both in having the generator, but also in knowing that I can count on Konsker to get it right and stand behind their work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Gainer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIvHVmU3eDfBfAoiR_T5QI4NqOJ7gXjJ03PNUHuMooUUCyQDvi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Rob on a Wednesday afternoon because I accidentally cut both hi and low voltage outdoor wires in the ground. He responded right away and came out on Friday morning. He figured out a complex wire situation quickly and had the wires replaced that day. I'm really pleased with the quality of work and the quality of his workers.  I plan to use him whenever I need electrical work. I highly recommend you use them too!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nanci Froemming","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQoZncJCWSQs04qWVh3wyDwPs3da1QK22_Al9wymbhBtRHKBM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Robert Konsker is an angel! The day after Christmas my thermostat quit working. I called several electricians and Robert was the only one who answered my distress call. Over the phone, he walked me through which circuit breaker to turn off to avoid a possible fire. While he couldn’t send an electrician to my house til the next day, his help relieved a lot of anxiety. He was so kind to spend time with me on the phone, at no cost.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Strauss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6NJW8l_TPw0EHnXsb_iekp9orIPsFV3r3FK-rLFy7onI9s8Fe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have hired Konsker Electric to complete a variety of electrical projects in my home; I recommended him to an apartment manager to do the work at a 75-unit multi-family building to replace all the main services and all the apartment sub-panels. His work was top-notch and reasonably priced. Robert and his crew are competent, reliable, trustworthy, do great work, and have pride in their work. Robert is a one-of-a-kind guy who has expertise in many areas.  I call Robert whenever I need services that Konsker Electric offers. I highly recommend using Konsker electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Nudelman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLguhNf6GljZBVSzzGhLnrejgjq2JDuJTaBqTIUmx2VzDGmrA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend! We contacted Konsker over the 4th of July weekend because our electricity had been cut off when a large tree branch fell on the line and damaged the connection late Saturday night. Konsker was out within an hour Sunday to assess, back Monday to fix the issue, and coordinated with the city for permitting and reconnection all by Monday afternoon. They were highly responsive, clearly did great work as the city signed off and said it looked \"perfect,\" and I found their rates extremely reasonable. Very pleased and we'll certainly call again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"rindee ashcraft","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEG6c3YzslxFMlB-rBh6-Aa_jKXPqqn5Y3Exm7mBjUQmHMzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We called about a set of outlets that wasn’t working- an obvious hunting job that other companies had already spent 2+ hours and hadn’t fixed. Konsker came out the same day, the person was so polite! He found the problem and fixed it and now my outlets work. A job well done with little fuss, we will be calling them for all future needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia Lippens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLn1vhoRCATyTEpHRJTns4BJpx6hlzsrRhLdvZYbzIwIvNSOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have worked Konsker Electric on a large scale project for our home. Robert and his team of experienced electricians were Reliable, experienced, and had a can-do attitude every single day that they showed up on the job. Throughout the project, Robert managed and oversaw all components- And his team was exactly what you would hope for on any project you are managing… they show up when they’re gonna show up, they do a good job, and they all have great attitudes!  Also, from a budgetary process Robert is very thorough on tracking hours With no superfluous billing… I would highly recommend working with them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Rudig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGhgvgB-FOzFsFmypFpyGiy65yeOe-hvLLMktQySHaC4Z5HZc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have hired Konsker twice in the past 6 months for different projects.  Robert is quick to respond,  a great communicator and resourceful.  All of the staff that came out were knowledgeable, efficient and professional.  Great experience and would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}]