ZngBt9GIf3FpdGCriS2VzAvg=w224-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"118203155244275172064","name":"Mauro Electric (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118203155244275172064"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"319 169th St SW","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98012","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kathryn Bernhardt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtdXNz5TLsXk7pZ1AwlOXhqKQrLAyQNuIYj-DepmMjT8MDeGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would give Mauro 10 stars if I could. I have a Briggs and Stratton standby generator. In the last storm it didn't fire up. I called every electrician (I thought) including the Briggs and Stratton authorized service centers. No one would even come out and look at it. The only option I was given was to spend between $18000- $26000 on a new generator.  I finally accepted that I had to purchase a new generator and was about to accept a quote when Facebook (first time I was glad that they listen in to conversations) displayed an ad for Mauro Electric. They had amazing reviews so I thought I would get a quote from them for a new generator. When emailing they responded and asked why I wanted a new generator I explained no one would come look at my Briggs and Stratton and I couldn't figure out what was wrong. They came out 2 days later - I needed a good cleaning/servicing and a new battery.  They could have been like every other electrician I called and sold me a brand new generator. Instead, they approached my situation with honesty and integrity.  In total I spent about $700 repairing my generator. Thank you Mauro Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Naab","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJw01LdqEwHHGVWo_U0fzPDDohAR6NJoMyrWGn5-DqEVmRZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really pleased with Mauro Electric today. The communications before the visit was without a glitch. Edwin was on time, extremely friendly, and professional. I was impressed with his listening skills as he was able to repeat what was important to us with regards to our roadmap. The team fixed our intermittent bathroom fan with ease. It was refreshing to meet such kind and skilled workers. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Irina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfjdRRayFqoS9mN7IGnLJADH9gUVpBBBAEmZwIo4c8Jayb4bEaZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience from start to finish. The free quote was quick and clear, and communication was easy and straightforward. The electricians were friendly, professional, and clearly knew what they were doing. They did a great job and left everything clean and tidy. Really easy to work with and highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allan Y.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkND588Td6WRFvSezQw87E_Cb6hQbCgxu0CDrM0Yk2jy00gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am truly impressed with the team from Mauro Electric.  From the estimate to the installation, the process was smooth and problem free.  The estimate was very reasonable, and scheduling was quick.  The technician Edwin A. was very professional, hardworking, and had the details of my needs communicated to him.  This resulted in a great finished project and a worry-free approval from Labor and Industries (permitting agency).  I would definitely recommend them to others as well as any additional electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Shapiro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhJhWCl-GouywMe9txF0kl7N0CWrGwGCK3MbxImxAGUL9AjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Truly, we are beyond delighted with the service and care we received from Mauro Electric. Ricky Mauro came to assess our under-kitchen-cabinet lighting electrical problem, and he was so kind, focused, and immediately discerning of the problem and perceptive about the solution. Then he sent Orlando and a colleague to come make the repair, and they, too, were kindly communicative, thoughtful, and amazingly effective at getting our kitchen lighting better than it was before. Of course, the price for this work was right, too, but the main point is Mauro Electric leads with its humanity, and that makes such a difference when compared with the other options. We are grateful for your care, Mauro Electric, and we recommend you to everyone who needs electrical services in the Seattle area. Thank you. So much.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2TR830f7j0tqIPpsClwsSiCPLDs6-MzyCQLWKdbz7XvENN_W37Vy7YUpqpfWgF_9F8L0ksacYkUgr1HAgZ0FLQKljDpCQWRr_wIqM-fFRKh7nFSsTjOEiWgQnG7l_x0h_Og3M4=k-no"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"John Lapsansky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-crPl-qXTDk75iYl3EI_sNGbCYShZmaVZeUfrUlk3FPT0EvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The quote was very fair. They were willing to work with me on the project. I would recommend them and will use them in the future.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3gcKSYk7lvBrxAvWAbUqfjY3tW13LYHQmKk9NgD7Rx7WlbpxWJPQq2nftm4GfLhrMRt4OKPp7niHJSQEx7j7b5rYk0k74AwYB3D2v8Y3RctzFDjCKmVQI2xPDytfMRJO2E3399HPHVoQQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-25"},{"Name":"philip laub","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_HW9LI368Pn0xmX9siHxCbnkgCAk0xLXBO1UMZvmaDJliFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I selected Mauro Electric to install a Generac Generator. They did an excellent job all the way through-competitive pricing, on time all the time, great communications and very professional. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hiral Bhatt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQzGNbrUy9W7-NEUAbChcoHGkdsA9wPxoq7sPw3LfdJkDWvXsq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Mauro Electric for multiple jobs for our home that included 1) Electric panel upgrade 2) Install two ceiling fans replacing light fixture 3) Upgrade old bathroom bent fan to bluetooth fan 4) Install EV 50A charger in Garage 5) Add socket for a dedicated Smart Toilet 6) Add socket for Smart Water leak detector.\n\nI loved their service right from the start to finish.\nI had invited multiple bids for the project and Mauro Electric's assessment of my project was at a great price and came with highly detailed explanation with their estimate.\n\nWhat I loved about Mauro Electric is their insight on meeting the city code and especially understanding the risk of not doing it right. Following was the eye-opener from Mauro's wisdom books.\n\nFor example, most homes do not have light fixtures in the bedrooms capable of installing a ceiling fan. I thought I could do this job myself watching some youtube videos. Trust me, not worth the risk and the pain.  It took 2 members of their team good 2.5-3 hours to install ceiling fans in 2 bedrooms that required them to install mount brackets by making several adjustments from attic.\n\nAs for Bidet (Smart Toilet), I had another revelation that I wasn't aware of. It requires 20A dedicated circuit breaker wiring to meet the code. I was planning to just jump extra connection from existing outlet. Could have backfired as smart toilets use significant energy for seat/water heating. You don't want the circuit to trip while using it.\n\nI was well advised for my EV car charger as well. The differences of level 1,2 chargers, hard wiring etc. and how market is moving forward in the future. Great insight.\n\nThe service team under  Ricky M. and Daniel Dominguez have delivered nothing less than fantastic output for all of the jobs they executed. The cherry on the top was their guarantee on the all of the work they delivered for my home that lasts at least a year and even beyond if they don't meet their highest quality promise.\n\nI must add that I am DIY enthusiastic but for the jobs mentioned for this review must have a licensed electrician like Mauro Electric to do it right and do it well. Highly recommend them.\nDeserving 5 Stars!!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17YVP8DY6uw_hJ7mj9y2zXr2Np-COlTDiyP5r4i6QHGuVPowZsfF9QIK-p-EUmHr-wQH4yhCSKwIRu6Cnvy93SWhs5QZZOqfArGJLOTJ3eZPthuWfKEhGjYd-FAp0m8E6ggiMY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0q00nQiw393SPn4sI1C7gEl852ItOJsIyWMXl0Y08P1KGjlhwxj5eH5o3dlAVcBTE6PfKEzKYS-mWEwvSPjqAGcOfBINk8zKCLYktiQUpI_hKgF7f7ASBvHEgF6TWRov-DZJouhA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn287z-TrcdGzyS0xbxcyo7SjBbpKK_jXDDug_9fkzTTJSteNfFwY2Vqha0flzXK5udKmu4A4_Ta-Ax4Roug6HT97zfscqRcgv30Jdy-UGanmClfjIqA66sp4Q--dRnZgCZ1pbc=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn34X9PSXe_L-9oeIX_mGE_08t805bQBB1rI4gMWOkO3LqdTutbaOUu01T3uiKxt-6cCobU8Ih95rAbMzrHZicaVWzcOiJ_vj8TTZgYdRv5a-8NCATLq4QZGub9xeXg8rLFfLvaP5g=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-2"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
