k in the future. Overall, it was a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zara Green","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcGskSIIcaerP8HuUS9_9T1WcKWUBh_Gzbc1MD6Gey3QsC7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hired the emergency electrician to install our new light fixture and they did a great job! The men were very professional and did an amazing job installing everything. They were very knowledgeable in what they were doing, so I was confident that everything would be up to code for the future. I also loved that it was over half off of the original estimate price!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Henry Chism","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWahnryL0tRIwEEmC0-0EudhXJ1S_7bEtPadynH3PkiTGcyjbtI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm not exactly sure what this business is because when I called the number listed my call was forwarded to Blue Flame Heating, Air, \u0026 Electric, (so really this review is for them). I had Thomas W. from Blue Flame dispatched to my home for a diagnostic call on an open neutral somewhere on one of my kitchen circuits (this was for electrical only no HVAC). He found the problem quickly, was able to repair it in no time, and educated me on how everything was wired up at the end. Very professional service and friendly, would recommend to anyone. Thanks again Thomas!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_TI-fmo-JmXnjCDUQV95R5R3PK9oSWWZGFl6HbD3Akc0LFeA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Regarding electrical work, I have the highest regard for them. From the receptionist who received my request to the electrician who promptly restored my electrical plug and switch, every aspect of their service impressed and delighted me. He was outstanding; he was extremely courteous and competent. My electrical issue was properly handled due to his meticulousness.","Images":null,"When"