EE0bXYwriOyJsB0dw43lZ-ThwtQvj-6Szg3McQpc38BcvUvDA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1A55l1tsFpYULPd--38evhVteQnY_pZsWqasXWJWXh9uTiN5zQOOwllHZdLvgP0w_RhICORU5csFjVciGDbOzzgyrR7qguV2kZoeSSKa7K8BKqDMctgxOLCJR1NrNnMgcdmvm-7Y9zJu4=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-21"},{"Name":"Alysha Yeamans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhbjjj1LQCA38oI8lMqfTM798-fAAZfZNhgxFlj-y-EFpyvW5C=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the second time I have used Dadz Electric and, once again, why they prove why they have such an impressive set of reviews. Not only did they respond and get me on the schedule quickly, but Igor went above and beyond to fix my light switches/circuit breaker and double checking to make sure everything was safe and functioning before he left. Pricing was extremely fair and Igor was incredibly knowledgeable and efficient! Will continue to use and recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ian Fournie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW80SGyOXoSY7Bh0B85wCcjFheeIoO0oK_xffQ7EwgnehlbYP9v=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had new appliances installed and there was a complication with the wiring for the new induction stove. The installers are not able to do any electrical work onsite, so I needed to get an electrician on board to be able to complete the installation.\n\nDad’z had upgraded my electrical panel a year ago and done an awesome job, so I immediately reached out to them and explained the situation and the need for urgency to reschedule the install.\n\nMo called me back, verified the circumstances and was able to to have someone come out the next morning at 8AM. Mathew arrived on time, assessed the situation and was able to make the remedies needed. He also noticed that that overhead vent unit and light were connected to the same circuit as the stove, which is not common practice or code compliant. He was able to come\nUp with a solution to complete the installation up to code requirements and keep my home safe.\n\nI like supporting local businesses, and I would highly recommend Dad’z Electrical for any home electrical repairs you may need-large or small. They are responsive, reliable, creative and thorough. They are now my “go to” electrical resource. Give them a try, you won’t be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Purcell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXnLavOfZNyXhzHLTdknQQhQvGkd2jc-wxb03ydLp5trePbgI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a panel and a meter box changed out. The work was excellent and the bill was fair. Very nice people to work with. They were  efficient and courteous.  I wish they didn’t outsource their office work. I was given 3 different numbers and confused where to contact. One invoice came from an email address that did not have ‘Dadz Electric’ in it so I deleted it. Small negative for the great work they did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phong Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTlMIa8X7jw2lg1QUvs8H7MtV7n7QWvIgDH0V1AtqyUVnDoCiNLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of working with Dadz Electric, and they absolutely lived up to their incredible Google 5.0-star reputation. As a business owner myself, I know how difficult it is to maintain that level of service across every job, but Dadz Electric showed me exactly how they’ve earned it.\n\nMatt, one of the owners, was great to work with—professional, responsive, and straightforward. Their pricing was fair and transparent, and there were no surprises—just quality work from start to finish.\n\nMo and Josh, the electricians who came out, were fantastic. They worked efficiently, wasted no time, and completed the job in half the expected time—which even saved me from having to extend my scissor lift rental. What really stood out was how highly the electricians spoke of their company and their boss. As someone who leads a team myself, I know that when employees speak that well of their leadership, it’s a direct reflection of the company’s values and the way they treat their people. That respect and pride came through in the work they did.\n\nI also noticed in other reviews that customers consistently praise Dadz Electric for being responsive, professional, and easy to communicate with—something I experienced firsthand. Their team truly cares about getting the job done right the first time, and that level of care is hard to come by these days.\n\nI’ll definitely be calling Dadz Electric for all of my electrical needs—both for my home and my business—and I won’t hesitate to refer them to all my friends and family. It’s rare to find a company this reliable and committed to great service.\n\nThank you, Dadz Electric, for setting the bar so high!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1YNnLFPClLWEk_GHagB7194uI6TgnbbuukdwSyhbV5LiVUdU3Va14tPUw5Rqr4Jbyb6lgUqKjbd9w53mWzYEP3DWCFhQXnSCQRPKoXVGsAN4Dn0ipMV_MTTDJEelnKYZA45hY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn10vEmkSqSLBqYODwi5N5GGGYJtsM6Lv_ZmZeR-ECa3xu4PZ4yarLf0kEJq4mNADLXcyLzVTqqa--YH37RSSl3IQyGGh6fPtfwUfoMXhWZeSfaEbSvBe5P7oD7yX0OWcTJlb4tw1Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn00Q8EYOzGgxRGyBy8-RrS1cxI37y1mdjuHEs3dJu_Qu37zdyMtigYTelol080AHx80CsuKoTxn94kltQxetOvMxvSm89not36em3E9jR7iDtgQPqe_04hWToffVWF49KiIQgk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2QnlumZ-39BxB8Wj7y28FUdjOJLiL_oWx-ogBOD2gLC5WNbwDIZ8HAZYWCZZALghV3qVFR9pay2749wX3VK-9xW90rrTialIPpIN4N8p6OiGkFDyahOAaca0PQRbN3eNJwH4CjLg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lPGROIq_Ma1q_c9BsKulm3vihGwDHSnXlJt1inCHwltSsS3wCrPaHFVw6WZEY5ze3l2JZIspt6p3kWGBPjtXAiUAo0ldAyMPKWoNzHph3JLPuRwPXVY_nL9V1MAMu8zi4Q3YJ=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-25"},{"Name":"Susan Hofacker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtLLm1hw4o4QVpXDDkJZJi3YgY6ixAy5kT-BZmHX1F5KajWEbi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional experience with Dadz Electrical Services LLC. Mo provided the estimate to replace our electrical panels, showed up on time, and offered a very fair price.  We scheduled a full panel replacement with the ability to add a generator in the future.  The office scheduled Josh as the electrician, he arrived on time, was very knowledgeable, completed the main work and inspection in one day and clearly explained everything he did. Everyone we interacted with did an excellent job.  I would highly recommend Dadz.   electrical panels replacement completed July 2025.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaimee English","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8bI0cwV2y0FQzsVPx3dI-jpBnT-AnHlbkyGK0YXk3cToKlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We installed a new heater ourselves to replace an old one, and we did it wrong! We then hired Dadz electric to come and double check that things ended up correct with the final heater install. They did that and made sure everything was correct and safe. They were able to get us an appointment quicker quickly and they gave us immeasurable peace of mind after checking and double checking everything. We will definitely hire them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gauntt Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdEGsoMspqQnzOx58oeWyUxY0A47xpyd4dL7hH7RNN1SdQKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the folks at Dadz were great. We had them install a bigger exhaust fan in our bathroom. It was a small job but Dadz service was great at every step of the process. From scheduling the service, to getting an estimate, to keeping us updated on arrival time; they excelled. They were clear and helpful with all communications. The installers were professional, answered all my questions, and did a great job. I would highly recommend Dadz and they will be the first and only call for any future electrical work I need done.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
