nal and down to earth guys.\n\nAll the work was completed to a very high standard.\n\nHighly recommended and any electrical work I need going forward will be to this company. I've already recommended them to a work colleague.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12vxg6dTGVqOzDeVW8mzll-ZAZx0Y4IKp6aSs4_iPI9ISXQGDroypujlC5-xh5Le_RuUN8ZJTOPVxQ4ImRDzJ-D-Ozbwi9jUFlnp5b6GkeofbneerDsIRvbqrGTNiiAmUuIJDAogzOyW8d=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2tg92Ww59T_RZ9ES1ai7YrvJ85kWFGfBQo345OcNBUEH06qvsX2h-s9ESVTKL-6bG8HgmBYJztfhC-3-Ul2ngeKwlxOQSlEdvCqhNRS0Mhgo4cnH21sDia0Q6UBSYk5K8B8oMomeRagprk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LqahFe_J_xBEZ88C1DAbFGiaMMEOmTSoClpeF_Yuz-CHMNqOWCTc0lIirpYaH2eRq9xoOrL_8Kiwx3wJvqC67h5va3uFKMatfrPOheGE5PTp-s5NZpkW9HGnbHUvq5IQ16NR2dnLKvNH8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1sc0dUAqsx-_hRiM_yYHQovHWIAP7z6NsJ1XxfKzY1VC1o9VjpLJdrAUinFY2LvGqjhwQ-qaI7hAhpba3zvYPMLhC0I-nHE95ZTiNbBSYaHhuflHjSvgWX7TeWkTXhKHdC9XXOq3rVpEYp=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-22"},{"Name":"James W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmANFa9Mgzl9ydlNuYhRwrc6wc_omIhCe6ycl15I-pr0mUm4ql=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Troy and Kadin installed a manual transfer switch with a mechanical interlock to safely attach a portable generator to my  home electrical panel during power outages. They arrived at the appointed time, worked quickly and professionally, and completed the installation at the cost promised, which was very reasonable. They then taught me how to properly and safely use the plug and switches they had installed.\nWhen the generator I had ordered arrived, I discovered it needed a different type of plug than the one they had installed. I called Troy and he and Kayden came the next day and changed the receptacle for me at no additional cost. I couldn’t be more satisfied with their services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jason tanabe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiCoFNr6GXb0X1DVCgxysdGgNhRFLa2yOIGA0Ivhm6SKg7gP3i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an EV charger installed by them and didn't have any issues. The install location was far from the breaker, but they were able to do it in a few hours. They were efficient and professional.\n\nGot many different quotes for this install and their pricing was very fair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TC LO","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAQCFctfRNTxOXkVh3qPYebnzXnTq6RP54SyOiTt885Gm8vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Troy who came to provide the price quote was very knowledgeable and even took the time to share extra information with me. Later, I scheduled a project for outlet replacements and light installation. The technicians, Kadin and his colleague, completed the job efficiently and with great quality. I’ll definitely call them again for my next project.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Kivi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXO8ENNvgSOzf6q4ou_CEgEzvc8DYhsHYoNYqKfCs8di1JlXTQcUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This morning around 4am woke up due to being cold. Attempted to reset circuit went to AI which listed a couple of nearby reliable electricians. Left a message at 'In Charge Home Electric' to see if they could fit me into their schedule. It was past 8:00am so we scheduled for 10:00. Troy arrived and diagnosed the problem, fixed it, educated me on how to prevent further problems and I'm writing this review at 10:40.\nI had overloaded the circuit with a portable heater and electric blanket. The plug in was fried and if not for the circuit breaker I would have woke up to flames or not woking up at all, along with my neighbors since we live in a multi-family home.\nTo say I am grateful is an incredible understatement and we will be getting all of our electrical work done by this company.\nI highly recommend 'In Charge Home Electric' for whatever small or large electric needs you might have.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dameon LaRouge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6IFCvrw3uqMlhrZg36T0Qn9R_gzA-W1WuI_mUS355K1CfGts=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ONE OF THE BEST CONTRACTING EXPERIENCES I HAVE EVER HAD. Amazing, prompt, knowledgeable, and respectful! Had 2 bathroom wall lamps that went out and didn't have the skill to put them up. They replied right away, inquired about the project and pictures, and were able to come by in a few days! On time and wonderful communication, and such an asset to the WA state electrical community. In and out in an HOUR, took out all the packaging from the new lamps, got rid of the old, just was an absolute joy to have in my home. 20 outta ten, would call again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Mp75NEGilk5rlwI_KwJ15ZMreZU5NQPu4zPgEaDXUHm7jjGyos0zTEYo3JlRaYOG9v3-bnP-2logY8Z0Dk5Xj8QZJCNGSaxxge6CCh27uMFk-MK-cX7fLsI_o8tSuuYYM-Ktv=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"MIKE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4JquuRhLrtlOr_gqVF-17JZVDxyYqvvpHKukM2It9EF53AQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This company was refreshingly professional because they not only listened, but they cared. Great follow through. Great scheduling. Great crew...AND...always on time! Exceptional!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali Piyarali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGXHzjdu_0pijiFMqiBM1fHYgicKVTe9dWqnHP0XccqsQzMJm6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely efficient. We had them coming and work around the house on a number of projects. Got it done on TIME. We had an small follow up issue and they came back right away to fix it...i love the fact that they stand behind their work. No fuss no muss !","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
