endly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Quincy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqGMYA4wfxe2VGTRq_VXjzeMxmJd-zwe3dENWOM5wOl0lVOB7f=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great company A/C and Heating. Since installation 2 years ago everything including maintenance was done professionally and with great communication  when needed. Staff is friendly and efficient. The techs are awesome. Max gets 5 stars for service professionalism, and trustworthy. I highly recommend Alpha","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yashar AB","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrSSdK8La5wV4YXjNWNBZvEjff0tIxz1bWnQ_DeGCZJN0RVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Max gave us a very competitive price compared to other HVAC companies. Explained very well the HVAC system we need. Installation appointment was very easy. On time crew arrivedd. Tom and Steve did an excellent job.  Very thorough and clean and will answer all your question. Owner is very accommodating and helpful through out the whole installation. very satisfied with the job and highly recommendable.  Thank you very much.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Babageldi Mamedow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOorx23AR_wCOM0WJGN_ft2tWfhjEWv5QySEVoU6ChZCv6Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Top-notch HVAC service! The technician was friendly, efficient, and explained everything clearly. The work was done quickly and professionally, and our system is working better than ever. Great experience all around — would definitely use them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJE2IRumYVNKah15C6Estpfst0gi5lj-rWVtN4HqMSUYBgiHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently hired Max and the Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric team to rewire an entire house and complete an electrical panel upgrade. They were outstanding from start to finish. Their deep understanding of electrical work—combined with knowledge of other aspects of construction—allowed them to recommend the smartest and safest solutions for an older home.\nThey were extremely responsive, professional, and positive throughout a very stressful phase of our remodel. The panel upgrade and rewiring were done cleanly, efficiently, and to a high standard. We couldn’t be happier with the results and would absolutely recommend Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric to anyone needing serious electrical work done right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yoma Pinkman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmERo0g1tCWEyD7WT1xIzCp2fPDseMB3dw_mSvN0V44dVVsEtA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I couldn’t be happier with my new home HVAC system from Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric. From the initial quote to the final installation, everything was handled professionally and smoothly. What could have been a stressful upgrade turned into a very positive experience.\nWhy I’m thrilled:\n•    Clear, honest pricing with a competitive quote — no surprise fees or upsells.\n•    Fast scheduling and punctual technicians who arrived prepared and ready to work.\n•    Clean, professional installation: floors were protected, work was done carefully, and the area was left spotless.\n•    The technicians took the time to explain how the new air conditioner and heater work, walked me through the thermostat settings, and tested everything thoroughly before leaving.\n•    The system runs quietly and provides even cooling and heating throughout the house. Energy efficiency was a major reason for my upgrade, and I’ve already noticed improved power usage.\n•    Warranty details were clearly explained, all paperwork and manuals were provided, and follow-up communication was prompt and friendly when I had a quick question after installation.\nOverall impression: Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric has knowledgeable staff, excellent workmanship, and installs reliable, high-quality systems. It’s great to finally have a comfortable home climate that works exactly as promised. I highly recommend Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric to anyone considering a new air conditioner or heating system.\n⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Five stars — well deserved!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Meylis Jumahanov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJCuxSVqEoLLYvRnEchbhci7hpU2FXG-xQEvz1ReW6AxfbiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience! Fast response, honest pricing, and quality workmanship. The crew was respectful of our home and made sure everything was running perfectly before they left. Highly recommend for any heating or cooling needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doni Gem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYP0CZHpVjWCTtKVOQO0jHXqa52TGibuald5PpMxeXfmwCjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m very happy and impressed with the furnace replacement done by Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric, recommended by John. I chose a heat pump system with no more gas hookup for the furnace, including new ducting.\n\nThe installation team truly respected my home. The pride they showed in their work was clear—the installation was clean, professional, and well organized. I’m glad I chose Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric, and I really appreciated the help securing great financing for the project.\n\nI highly recommend Alpha HVAC \u0026 Electric for their honest approach and fair HVAC replacement quotes.\nThanks! From one happy customer.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kim Mulvehill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDlWDGJejfXtYNmNFs6LZhjcEX4O5bdXMV9AeaRy6PtdeWDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Max and his team were an absolute breeze to work with from the beginning and we highly recommend them. We initially needed an electrical panel upgrade to be able to install air conditioning, which he did promptly to keep our project moving. He was so professional that we hired him to do the electrical in the rest of our house for our remodel which included new switches, new outlets, new lights, new bathroom fans, new exterior lights as well as under cabinet lighting. He was very affordable and even had great recommendations for light and outlet placement to ensure that we met Kirkland’s code requirements and had added convenience in our home. Max and his team were super friendly, great communicators, and were very reliable making multiple visits throughout our project. Hiring them was worth every penny and we definitely plan to call them for our next project. If you want excellent service, peace of mind, hire Max and his team!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
