":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3-d-UdyS7l8dNYkVVvU9fg8zpreXjYiBLqLxP1yIXJwOyFVULVTeh2WJSA_3r4K-0fTeZpcXKFfivapgLYP-PiPGQDm3ruAok7MGGTrNygiHadeFa1aR1j_Z7cGY-EAbXVv0mF5EVdpSDW=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-6"},{"Name":"Robert Gay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNN6hw_r9XLd56yjixY5E7JRxb_bpKDYpNdTYpaJ3A0KNUJWFT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Replaced old AC and furnace with variable heat pump and 2-stage furnace. Also put dual head mini split in addition with no forced air and upstairs living space with minimal ducted air. House feels amazing now and perfectly balanced. Very professional, techs were friendly and easy to approach and make suggestions to. Laura was great in sales and not pushy, was very knowledgeable and communicative throughout the process, and provided useful applicable deals that pushed them over the edge over other bids. So far very happy!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1tzhFbD_UGZ6IzZ_iYrbqKVALmbyL3JKn0_S2EVZprDcbPh7FFCmb8-1JibvFzBcw3oUvbHTGHyqf37uPrTnqwUCbuEQ6oPsWSlbP-KK2fTOCwNLU3Lf3cBxP6JXG8vkzQdk_k-Vw12ZDl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MZIWClCTOkv6ArPzBnxnOPoeqAIYIu6fev-C-Jsg5tg7WriYpamnjF79MqLBthWH3AzULnlbR_q_Pg2MNP13PCjZwxI13CZd4X_bJPTTqYSP01v9r9yiHTe-rBcciO_KJJvqAfAY2zdxo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1DxqCPkmtPWatg_8C2TKT3kwEy7KxO9cy8_9mUiuKHamVtfLw67QImOwEVpZa8qoCTsfhFk9H2F_bYAysACzntPoldnD2vthuvHKu8JrHaoog7ngzX2u9XI-zAb-FHWBCWJILmS4xS5wJv=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-28"},{"Name":"Erich Rau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQgKFBtMWZpuH2SGpx19fporSFhuQmOyEicFBloZDlBE1tvrv4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Oscar is a great professional and also very friendly and easy to talk to. He’s worked with us twice now and I would be happy if he handled the majority of our electrical needs going forward! This most recent visit was a minor warranty call so we didn’t owe anything