aluate our heater.  Additionally, he inspected the vents inside our home after completing heater maintenance.  Thanks, Jeff.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0OSRwlJfkFB06cAHGKZLDE-qrPF9uQsiBheQnOQsOAQop6HSGFXaPnC9_OzM6GzBhmRWSKSAXuzKTk7VP_YllfET-QPZ9PwRDeiFROuLPIoCJaMxu3iKMNm8ryWW1V4bBrSda_OYHf1mo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0gOqAtloIcj8mK9hM-uzfvyXyDNwcLh9cNQpPXhfIQ6bX19U8w9gyRY4J2Kj4igVk9uivj_k1t_AlZqVfEJswYmf-FFgpWfywm8uccQIgZYzvCC-47Bz06CwQuxLFIHQl4wUNx3htob3E=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1rNKvIJ37vY3o9f0L64MbbLPVCN_6imX2cQmJrrQTb_dtU7B3YB8WvEU1wLHqyOwfWlJkZlbgNUU5xlIaaN9QmC5o1JoG5aiggKRzEZrdYSKI-WzyGMc9dZam_YMXtPMQ2FbCJS030aKE=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-11"},{"Name":"Priyanka Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLojl-A837LiJ5iC08RMnmRsAB6-CGi6BRJ9pIzPBwv_dcd6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Oscar and Kyle did a great job. They got the work done efficiently. They explained things clearly and made the whole process easy and stress-free. I’d definitely recommend them.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IKOGYr46m_tttNPM1rYyaVVWpELXPjsUcwvQ2qQa1yumOI-PCUyZANHnBy6E6i1YiijsLY5kAaJiBswrngH6QARHMGFX5DDYGB_P5GknD-lebza4tUnR_QnnGXKeNRZIpIxadddWVMKyk=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-16"},{"Name":"Johnnyband B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwdg-yt_M2ySQfMiRw_uxKoeZ2KhhM6I8-EXe3l7_inSMSdw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thomas K and Matier S came to our home and installed a new whole power panel. Their work was exceptional and they were very professional and very nice. I would absolutely recommend them for anyone that needs high quality and beautiful clean work done. BelRed is fortunate to have them working for them. I couldn’t be happier. They are pictured here with my wife.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0wqQg6mqDuC9OhoXD4VzlQ_B5h1Rr87kR_KjNb_I3Oh1kXRm73bbW8bE6