ed so badly or disrespectfully. When I reached out to you, I was told by the people on the phone that management had decided they did not want to speak with me and would not provide any details.\n\nIt seems that only after I submitted this feedback did you decide to engage in a positive manner. I sincerely hope you will be more mindful of the people you hire and how they communicate with your customers, especially when we are simply calling to understand and inquire about an issue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beka Deressa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKj8tEJDOr7jTE7nKrOpS6ZrheDYLLIDaaIxJYUXb5LUWbURQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I feel like I need to share my experience. Be aware of the diagnostic fee. They charge 163 dollars for a diagnostic fee. That seems odd, especially since it took them 5 minutes to diagnose. Then they charged almost 200 to repair. It took them 20 minutes to repair. I paid 307 dollars for a 20-40 minute job. Further. I called the night before. He said he would send someone out in the morning. He did not disclose the high diagnostic fee. At 11, I called for an ETA. They said the person I spoke to didn’t schedule it. The lady said they would have someone there between 1-3. At 3, I called for an ETA. The guy they scheduled had an emergency. Okay. Things happen, usually nice to let your customers know. They said a different persons coming after 4. That time changed to 5-7. I called again at 7. Someone finally showed up at 7:30 at night. Not great service and very expensive for what I got.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gracy Munoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVE0zw6pKE8PW2nM2Fk4rmcd8VimNlOoUBM_v6kCM0A3UU5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently needed help with installing an EV charging station in my home. I wanted to make sure I choose someone with experience and knowledge. I reached out to Jacob Electric and they were amazing. They were very helpful and gave me great prices. I will be definitely using them for any other electrical issues that I may have.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"De’Monte Sims","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgeKGZ-L_HHHOj5SXP_0ZW7gdhggYriUul-anvqV7U3WsVmYTL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very unprofessional they installed my charger incorrectly and now it’s overheating. They then told me they have to charge me to come check to see what the issue is . Horrible service and customer service: Update They came out because I called and told them it’s smoking they then claimed that this happened from over using a charger which is impossible I charge 1-2 times a week . They then proceeded to tell me this isn’t a wiring issue when the wires are clearly burned and fried don’t ever use them they are trash .","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3irx_Xe95dkcDNG_rzdl1LoOkLp_5WeaiEvIrjEV5-vJrZ8bsmvS9FSmrIZxkT6wgTc2sEmibTvgJZdHVE40KrIHiTgQZpuZKL7zHypOEe76boPKXqd_XWFYc1k4PgYJooU1kL=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1fCnPICIbiLe35ZSHibQPILaechzhTsZeRIQSARjkAHU2r2K7uT0mwMaP72bKtmMluwVz21iWxx9HM0XU0lOpuRgPtI8b76SRQt7lhPOUT8OTFRJAOaQssk3rnTHW5ZvslFL8DCw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0y1Mqz73sb0fip_BqkSJ-Qd6Ah5YyJZ8CS1nqFdq9UOOUrWZZS7sd-73HCuioarWKiayxYAg0aYGiVZrJly_zYB0pnvVjVDHAi11W0b2ZSZqSl7WuZBIsn7cbTOATwKaCLPGog=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0HfWv9knH1wyxrSIKpTO83Zs_aESTTafbgxhmFExQAqPf8Wax8_1GaLXnygCkyrMwZAvCg5VmdiP8K84GV0fXtz9g7IfZbC15bVA8pdOY8dazC0sRVLxYrfLEy3mXXS79bRZcU4A=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-24"},{"Name":"karrar azeez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5KuhYR2NlDvTO0O6GuQVpHxYgOf08mG1SVdABG0mp1gWN9Ten=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had really bad experience with them after I explained everything I need I had to travel outside the country when I left I came back. I found out the guy that was there to 