t-4th-systems/","source":"4thsystems.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"100090459996998072670","name":"4th Systems (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100090459996998072670"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Shorewood","street":"11235 26th Ave SW","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98146","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kat444","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPZYcCgT33W9ob-vhRyaoJhyFS3aLrDvNzRJ8zdHyjKe6g92K-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"4th Systems proved to be knowledgeable, fast and most importantly, trustworthy, when they optimized our internet and mesh WiFi configuration. Our internet speed had degraded to almost nothing in spite of paying for high speed service. After chasing our tails with multiple providers/equipment support teams, we were at a total loss. And with 2 home offices (one with VPN) that require consistent bandwith, our ability to work was impacted.\n\nThe 4th System folks carefully diagnosed the issue and fixed it quickly. Their knowledge of the systems and equipment was impressive. We appreciated the open communication and timeliness. We turned to them because they had previously fixed a home wiring issue as well as installing security lights and cameras. We were relieved that their expertise is broad.\n\nI highly recommend 4th Systems!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rafael","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSq_nZJJ9N9socKypi6Ky7IzOUsTbaW3efd8DOUHksi4KKwsaX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with 4th Systems. We had a continuously tripping circuit and they came out the next day to diagnose. Everything was explained very clearly and their work matched all estimates of time and cost. Haven't had any issues since, highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGcF3801-cSrGVxoinPIC_zyl_Cn6OxFTNa6rm4nfLmpqPgeqO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys get it! After a long and exhausting hunt for a quality contractor to help with our customer in the Seattle area for a security alarm installation, we were referred to 4th Systems.\n\nThe first call with Andrew and I knew we found the right place. He was pleasant to talk to, listened to what we were looking for, took time to understand budget knowing that we were subcontracting and lastly was able to work with us on a quick/tight window to get the installation done asap.\n\nAndrew delivered the quote promptly, we shipped the parts and he was installing in what seemed like less than a week turnaround. The client was happy with the installation and quality assurance is definitely part of their project management.\n\nIn closing out the project, I personally spoke with their President, Coleman to congratulate him on the teams job well done. We talked about collaboration and ability to work together in the future.\n\nI will definitely be calling these guys back. Not only did they help with our security install, they do so much more and are a full service electrical contractor.\n\nThank you Andrew and Coleman! Keep up the great work!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2xf_zyLSXody8tMNl-xumWFlr5YQbqecylBH7TAMFTzxywj4Wbm5_3dubR5hPWE7s38N7cSw9V9jeHzGjhxwm4k5e7uGUCf-WPklSBNZilrSEXRt5LZXnCs_1qJiIYLii7PHCJKA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Pe-mphRrcCdsmiRYWpgndrywEIp05BH6IGZIEq7ycmWh5ISJ62vEfdtjZW62hGYMguyZJeKVQN2rHlkNvJNJBWy9O2mJ5wk5G3c1rCvHauuBPMV-FNglDTuZbYHKOu04YbzGs=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-4"},{"Name":"Shawn Brockman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYXY474A5dKE1KkqsdEkoiyoZApFw3qkS1mc74hV_S4w-Pm9pDCg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Andrew from 4th Systems helped us sort out our home network in our tall townhome, and we’re really happy with the results. He cleaned up the messy wiring, everything looks sharp now, and the speeds are fast everywhere — even on the top floor. Super easy to work with and clearly knows his stuff. We’d definitely call Andrew and 4th Systems again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kylie Cave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWs4Vwiu5PXOPpUS7F0VQYSpGC0LmjeM5lnAS8Sg4yYyZBM65Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"4th Systems is a wonderful company. Their communication was fantastic. Everything was explained to us as needed. They were also super friendly and respectful. Even with the old chaotic wiring in our building, he was able to diagnose and fix our electrical problem within a few hours.  We greatly appreciate their help and would highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayla Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVF46hA5Tifq_vtQzeAuxMeXqC3WN_Qz_l8o8hM0Y0a6KfsegwJ-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience working with 4th Systems and would 100% recommend them to anyone needing electrical work. We hired them to install a dedicated circuit for our infrared sauna, and from start to finish, they were incredibly easy to work with. They were responsive, communicative, and made the whole process seamless, from the initial consultation to scheduling the work.\n\nThe installation itself was quick and efficient, completed in just a few hours with a small team, including the owner, who personally oversaw the project. They also made things even easier by handling the scheduling of our final inspection with the city of Seattle, working around our availability.\n\nSince the work was completed and inspected in January, we’ve been using our sauna every week and couldn’t be happier. 4th Systems’ professionalism, communication, and care throughout the process truly set them apart. We wouldn’t hesitate to work with them again for any future projects.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Chavez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzC17odAhREMOt__CweG-jImKPsGgYWoxPjbjDZn6HQ57Y7EQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I had just bought our first home that came with several first home \"quirks\" - improper wiring for large equipment, old lighting fixtures, etc. My brother had worked with Andrew from 4th Systems and highly recommended them. I'm so glad I went with them! Not only were they able to address all the immediate electrical concerns but they helped us upgrade fixtures and install a security system. Now our home feels much more updated, but more importantly they've helped give us peace of mind knowing the major issues have been addressed and we have a security system that's easy to use. Would absolutely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren Buck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUw6RENV1WgE6rLY-6mYBo3tChUFb3jPL1_JqrRgNLfAi58vE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"4th Systems did a great job installing the electrical required for EV charging at my rental home. They were flexible and accommodating throughout the process. I recommend them for your electrical needs!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
