schedule it to meet some changing circumstances on my end. I requested Brandon to do the work as he performed my previous job.  He also recommended a high quality toilet that worked in my situation. I was called and texted to let me know he was coming.   He was fantastic and explained how he was going to do the work and showed me the conditions of my existing connections. He got it done very quickly and efficiently and did not leave any mess. I’m super impressed with how this company operates.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn18mXxbzJFwSEfF_FxfY-aB9FnugpevApPIXoBy0xP7NbXLlqa41jlsASWKaHmzLCe7ZoqsrpX935a4oJbvnwq7LHO9fUifDkmuRPWKEKYS3ytaP6tG7QCRmzMUhBRUNRSAoKEUu8wuR-Qc=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3TO76XJuEWHeDAs50c3eHmsS-l0gnYvS11e85c0AuWg5SMQV2-WPeRoS0wOASLaCl1WKPxU1nRvKaRUeljHaKFeLFYiXPDlQmSw004jNzbzxahD3hQYalhhAaHABa5XlWACFKrOTCzsyww=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2QK_XUR4am5b1AToUnDHcugl8ZBTVgRHCvKaZqrPLl-qWMBwDmQK2QN7jrqqKtRHwZPjp33qOm30JbtM7uqYkltZiUC7peAKr5sWSwTGigK_WSVd1xGAyPcSf5RJJgCwvOrIJV3YCQ8CjE=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-23"},{"Name":"First Name","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImUkzESVcwtk6GN6YpQWav4WKEwy0irDjFSawAc-GirWB9V6xM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had 2 Sons out to replace a kitchen sink and faucet.  Brandon and Jack did an amazing job!! They worked diligently and quickly to get us back up and running.  They had to do some minor adjustments to make everything fit.  They made sure to keep everything clean and exceeded our expectations!  Can't beat this company and its workers.  We will be calling 2 Sons again.  Thank you so much!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1tl1SfKpOij1defEM3RKiSZlzKVPlPzkdUcgT7ZlS_tdKWfDP7SB0FGFYy3k7UZEcIk1pNA7W9uZup-5OJxAiuHoBXwSSGl7VUH4oOm_B7FYZ_Nh-ga6kRPyOOUp-IhBOAEskoHXWGVvs=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-28"},{"Name":"Kathy Cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEZheNcF1uUp9QLLEl6mRDckvK11gHbSq2W3OqX__v_-irKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have to say Bob was amazing!!! I had a clogged drain in my kitchen sink. Bob came in and took every precaution to be neat \u0026 clean. He explained to me what he was going to do and gave me the pricing and I agreed and he got to work. He was super kind and polite and fixed my drain issue. He was a pleasure to work with. I would highly recommend using 2 Sons!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DyAndreye Wray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHO7twmPtSOgt9fBIugfw1-LKd13Pj-ASuJdDIr2S7iA7y6ae9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Carey and Mycha came over to do some plumbing work at my residence and did an amazing job from beginning to end.\nI appreciate the great communication and great service and it was done in a timely fashion.  Thank you for the service \u0026 I look forward to doing business with you again!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xLOB19HYGZMFUt_t5K02J95JoeD17xwxYGpoL60TZtFM2USNqFRsmAl6hh27fGYAIXhF6-qNHg-tl1ensyX9hDQiRbk92qDlaG3_6jI7Ey13ClsWk8tIkq_36_fEUhsR3QLBWm3kArr_4=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-3"},{"Name":"Katy Garner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvmxb4ATPGKIGsuYPT7XjY1BqdJ4yJkqReMc7NMbYZxEaPbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a mystery leak per our meter reading. Riley and Riley saved the day.  They promptly discovered the issue, resolved and repaired our pipes in one service call.  They were quick, thorough and entirely delightful.  They took the time to talk me through the job.  I felt heard, safe and comfortable with the two of them in my house.  For my next plumbing disaster I hope to get ‘The Riley’s’; but know, whoever comes will be excellent.  Thanks 2 Sons!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Sutter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUq9ycA-YpQxXxsa5ghZzxAwasJIYeQ5jW-p4T8fx3oNKRzQAg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2 Sons are my go to plumbers and I recommend them to friends and family looking for a recommendation.\n2 Sons had my tenant's water heater replaced in the same day I called them!  Justin and his apprentice were awesome! This wasn't a \"quick\" replacement in the garage - they had to figure out how to squeeze in the water heater through a tight crawl space on their hands and knees under furnace ducting.\nJustin was knowledgeable and helpful in troubleshooting different replacement scenarios.  He was kind and patient with my number of questions.  He never once complained to me about the undesirable placement of the water heater under the house.  My tenant even commented to me how kind Justin was to her.\nThank you for making this a quick and easy fix!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Church V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvOjoE-NvQhJabipUPXF9w4Z5MhN9hTQ5O2sSOcp7vHID_W522=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We contacted these Plumbers on a Friday using Yelp quotes, and they were the fastest to reply and the fastest to engage with us when we had questions.  We felt that warranted to give them the opportunity to give us the first consultation.  Sometimes we get multiple consults if we get any icky feeling from the people doing it.  We didn’t feel that way with this company.\n\nOur toilet was leaking, and we expected we probably could use a new one.  But wanted a professional estimate and options.\n\nWe got hooked up with their team to schedule it and they were able to give us a time only a day out.  We asked for a 8-1pm window and received automated text and a formal phone call from a dispatcher saying how far out the plumber technician was.\n\nThe plumber who showed up was named Carey.  We also a received a picture of him before he arrived for safety concerns which I thought was a good touch of care from the company.  Carey was lights-out the best guy we could have asked for.\n\nHe showed up within the approximate eta and was kind, gracious, considerate of our space and gave us a myriad of options.  He quoted us prices that felt quite fair, and we chose the option where he removes the toilet and chooses a toilet for us: though we talked about the various options beforehand.\nAll and all he left for 30 min to get the toilet: and returned to install it.  Installation was complete within another 30 minutes.\n\nHe was so good man.  And we just felt like this is how service and care and things should be in this world.  It’s always refreshing when you get that.  Because so many outfits just: make you regret everything.\n\nThe work was quick, professional, and he was happy to be there and gave us information every step of the way that we respected and appreciated.\n\nWe will use this company in the future.  You earned our respect and business.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
