r_Z5EFe3nJHiMcmEXCta6GX7OE0CU95-juPr20oA5hk0XqiBdI466Rtip1r4=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-20"},{"Name":"Brian Szuter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwEpYQ8J9WoE_RQhzjoeOMorpF-MRneUaBhTXtycbPCUl6Ct2H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was impressed all around with Switch Electric. They did a great job replacing our electrical panel and adding a dedicated circuit for an induction range. They were easy to communicate with, easy to schedule, and were extremely responsive with the (very minor) issues the city inspector found. They ensured everything was up to code and I was impressed with how they handled scheduling the inspections on our behalf. I would use them again and recommend them to others.\nI can't really say if they offered a good price though - of the 5 places I called for the project, Switch Electric was the only one willing to give me an estimate.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K. Anthony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDrKL0kVEsZ6iJMIjiRdu7I2KKCpWq782P_nZRz1NDjpNqc4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Switch Electric to get several jobs done that I had been saving up since I moved into my new home. From the initial consult, right through to completing the work, the team was really great. They confirm what’s to be done, provide great information, check their work, answer questions, and clean up after themselves. I’ll definitely be using them in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeffrey Rosinek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV2IQa6InygOQqaXpA1Ky2SLc1MCGcyWywn8FJhkxuUGi91zFkPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another excellent experience with Switch Electric. My annual generator inspection went well and was cared for by a true professional. Very grateful to maintain that generator which has worked well when the electricity has gone off a number of times, especially this winter. I needed a new battery, which had not been replaced since we got the generator nearly 10 years ago. All in all I truly reasonable price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chuck Malmsten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjL1LxxlWlMADfsWyZZZIJEEK8lVkvJqakIl3J_C_-thL0iuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bryan, Tyler (and a 3rd electrician, sorry, I forgot his name) installed an Ecoflow Smart Home Panel 2, part of a whole house battery backup system. They arrived on time, had all the parts and tools they needed. They appreciated the diagrams I provided identifying the circuits (18) to be moved to the new sub-panel transfer switch. They evaluated the work area, came up with an installation plan, and got to work. They completed the job sooner than expected, tested the system, cleaned up, and labeled the new breakers. A job well done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sue Meza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgBrKXRHoNgE8x6L6iR0EINFFbPt209ZHlqEwjJ96MLhUiv4Tghg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The two guys that were here doing my generator install were timely, communicative, and respected our property. They cleaned up everything and made sure they communicated with me about what has been done. Now we’re just waiting for the city to do their inspection and they will get the generator hooked up to the gas line. I’m so happy that the next time it rains my sump pump will automatically come on even if there’s no power.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3bM7u1TNobVJs3cyecDx4J770BPiASTBc0ikgqVoBWU3T6icC77ebmG-iPLwN7m3nBJ3kxVpUyxm9NXTgT2TucPKSMKb-Ax1Oi-k9Q8NoCibym1ja9SuA6prGc7dmNiFAXi9aLRYANr67v=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BUa2Nk6L_F6ouOilCdrJz_GMg2td8rqD1LJ00X8oZOsCXQ9_W395j5AmHma0xo8BmPu3DYUY3m9iGrBdJ9WwzyYA7hk-YP7YFGpgtZB6_Uu7jIWFAfrpMizgYUYXvUYdkOK6WaDcjpWJx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn04-QoQzrwq05ayM067KRzWTICw7CwGttTKrxqUsqEk0OcJeb