Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Chris Jeakle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4St9QdK276kLRwOwCyw5yu5d4gDKakju4npyHJDsmliqeKd3h=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cisco Electric has been spectacular to work with!\n\nJackson, the electrician we worked with, is great. Riley, the person we planned the work with over email, is excellent, too.\n\nThey dealt with us anxious first time homeowners and helped us fix our biggest concerns.\n\nThe cost was very reasonable, the people we interacted with are great, and the work is great, too!\n\n* They are great communicators - planning was straight forward and clear\n* They are timely and reliable\n* They answered all of our questions, so we were confident in their project plan and judgement\n* They are incredibly thoughtful - everything was cleaned up and anything moved to do work was put back in exactly where it was\n* And of course, the work looks and works great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Palmeri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5m0-A5--FCe3TKZTEYtlvcy1LTK3zvWNKzKOcJmlqkSGFKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can't say enough about Cisco Electric. Their electrician Noel was very knowledgeable, professional and extremely hard working. He completed a number of tasks (ie; outlets, ceiling exhaust fan,\nreceptacles, etc.) in a single days work. Glad we went with by the hour charges based on his work ethic and his willingness to help.\nI recommend Cisco Electric and Noel and Frank for your Electrical needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharon C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtBKx5bpW2f6251eGR9p4x2_McPFfzJpwyZGazvISjWF8r79c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From start to finish, an exceptional experience. Frankie was detailed and cost conscious when he did my estimate and his technicians were thorough and skilled. Communication on every level was excellent - the organized way the project was planned and executed gave me confidence in their work. This was a large, three-day project that went down without a hitch. I strongly recommend Cisco!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kimberly Hobbs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSQwDKrtNdcHfhnsyTVLpkbKxHGqlxTyYUPjeTpEFd2GU5jZMxlw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The owner, Frankie Martinez, is a consummate professional. Frankie Martinez is a highly skilled and reliable electrician who has provided exceptional service to us for over 20 years. We have used his services to re-wire two homes and have always been impressed with his professionalism and dedication to ensuring that our best interests are met. Frankie's friendly disposition and commitment to old-fashioned service values are truly remarkable, and we always feel confident that we will receive the best quality work from him. In addition to his excellent workmanship, Frankie is a great communicator and is always responsive to our needs. As a Real Estate Broker, I have recommended Frankie to numerous clients, and they have all reported back with glowing reviews of his work and his team. Overall, I highly recommend Frankie Martinez to anyone in need of an electrician who is knowledgeable, trustworthy, and committed to providing the best service possible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lowell Neal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVR0xz5q6xR02ozIPDJ6yufkkKQ9AjoHHI02GMFQdpJ4AaiZWhg6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Cisco update the wiring in our attic from the old knob and tube to modern and code compliant.\nFrankie was easy to communicate with, timely, set proper expectations, did great work, checked and tested everything afterwards, and cleaned up leaving things better than he found them.  Is there anything more you could want in an electrician?  Or anyone working on your house for that matter?\nWould and will hire again without hesitation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL9fa0hRw41F4wqkFVhRg1xzWKrWMzsXCmNdoXxwqSO1yn8u05=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used Cisco for about four projects and one electrical repair over the past couple of years and they've been outstanding. Competitive pricing and very professional, attentive, and efficient staff. They've helped us install recessed led lighting, pendant lighting, new switches, bathroom fans, and new breaker in our Condo and everything's been beyond great. Thank you, Cisco!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julia Ednie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL32TWqSMKq4k7CVSPfqljUpBpyx2FDDrMVtSXZbdAOYX73Og=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an issue with some newly installed hardware in our house that caused our circuit connected to our furnace to trip continually. Frankie (owner of Cisco) heard our problem (no furnace in the winter!) and came himself right away as he didn’t have anyone else free right at that moment. He figured out the problem and a reasonable and efficient solution quickly so that we were up and running again with heat. I was very grateful for him coming through in a pinch like that. We have additional work to be done and we definitely plan to use Cisco for it!\n\nUpdate: we had the additional work done and are still just as happy with our experience with Cisco Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"zac corum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbHWNSUEUSqQMtt2ZP7x60X9L89TywoGtpD1E0_0w5PDvCpg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Frankie was recommended to us through a trusted friend (general contractor) several years ago to work on our West Seattle brick house that had outdated wiring. We have chipped away at our projects over the years and have hired him with success every time. Most recently he rewired our last few knob and tube outlets and fixtures while we were away on vacation and left the place spotless and worked judiciously to minimize the amount of drywall and painting work (and came in under budget).  Cisco just completed a job for our neighbor who had only good things to say.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
