ious and performed high quality workmanship. They paid great attention to detail and all the small things, including how gas lines and electrical wiring was routed and secured.  At the end of each day the work area was spotlessly clean.  The team also worked extremely well together - always helping each other out.  Lastly, they are all genuinely nice people.\n\nThis was our second major project with Pearce.  The heating and A/C group installed a new Bryant heat pump at our house about 18 months ago.  We had the same great experience with that installation, too.\n\nWe are extremely happy to be customers of Pearce!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurence Raybois","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlqTiYmnC6FVtVA5J-ClxmtuZ5rCbo0C88btQsgn-Wvna3oQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I could not be happier about the service I received today. My house is very old and there were multiple issues.  They were resourceful and worked all day on the various issues at hand, with a smile, and for a more than reasonable fee.  They went to great lengths to explain to me what they were doing and present the options to me.  They are definitely my go-to electricians now!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Feiyu Shi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxAntrALrvLOGglthlfCRryXMG90gn4YimrWaVaDcjMlEN748=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Pearce Electric for a panel replacement and installation of a generator inlet with an interlock switch, and the whole experience was excellent. Chris, Isaac, and Tim were all incredibly kind, knowledgeable, and patient — they answered every question I had and were very upfront about the process and options.\n\nTheir pricing was competitive and very reasonable for the high quality of work. The installation was done beautifully and neatly, and everything works perfectly. I also really appreciate their 3-year labor and general-use material warranty, which gives great peace of mind and shows how much they stand behind their work.\n\nHighly recommend Pearce Electric if you’re looking for a professional, honest, and skilled electrical team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eva Pei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM-VZhAt-EVWXYLHWWZ-1ViacjGzhw0qsfO9l5AIYYi1EY9wxc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We searched high and low for a reliable, honest, quality company who could update our furnace and install an AC system - and Pearce has been a dream to work with. Claire is a down-to-earth, friendly professional. They did a stellar job with the installation, we enjoy a comfortable home in the summer now and we have them come out to do regular maintenance. highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leslie Waters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbI3wd10-anSIuiJHQaGgoC5-XVcwnrbdDfAe5NF7iC7wpkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pearce Electric installed a generator for me and they were superb!  They arrived on time, worked quickly and professionally until the job was done.  They instructed us on how to operate the equipment and cleaned the area thoroughly before leaving.  I recommend them highly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracy Russett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZrur6J8JPmrNdYGUwzIVaLABtsqvKLPkCLkR-H_RLoMb1aA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with Pearce Heating and Cooling. They came out promptly and quickly fixed our furnace at a reasonable rate. Very happy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Royce Ferguson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLH19kPgHy5YoDZi-1XzbP-qDvt3JWiRoBtyi64wWQuTb7D4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pearce installed our AC unit 2 years ago.  They are still checking in with us, are still courteous over the telephone, and communicate promptly.  More, Claire just checked our unit and it’s working perfectly.  Claire