ar Power again for any work that needs to be done.  We are super appreciative! Thanks, James!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R Jansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrt8gqJrHJ-9XeBqp5kr2-EZgstp3vYIMWlAEindDLoD_eqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very pleased with the whole experience. James had great communication, was very knowledgeable and completed my job in a timely manner. I also appreciated how he kept the mess to an absolute minimum and cleaned up after himself. His price was more reasonable than the other electricians I recently hired.  I will definitely use him again. He was referred to me through my realtor. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saurabh Ajmera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgr7TwHDdy7DQZBVxHd1vAgL3etQQBXZqU4otTrxeeb9v5btm-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve hired James for a few electrical jobs, including installing my Tesla charger and several GFCI outlets around the house. He’s always on time, courteous, and clearly knows his work well. His prices are very reasonable, and the quality of his work has been excellent every time. I really appreciate his professionalism and reliability — highly recommend James for any electrical work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manoj Sarma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWExKa8DoYCWPDcPnPajzb8XywqTdf_FSz628gGuIFWq02gtsX1qg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hired James for installing an inlet for a generator and a GFCI outlet in the crawlspace. He was pleasant to work with, efficient and very professional. His estimate was also very reasonable relative to other quotes. He also took on additional work on the day of the job and charged reasonably for those as well. Would definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bethany R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpzvHzMoQ2gDY6Kuh9kmeVr2EfU1Kr6Xtz3GdJoAx3RKKuw-