Hill","street":"4133 15th Ave S","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98108","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Natalie Crowder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3HrEG0LQJzyyFz93WnLVXmj5U4VecK6fUa3tDBW7cl4-0bQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle was prompt \u0026 professional! He arrived just when he said he would, which I very much appreciated. I have been having trouble with a breaker for months. He investigated and was able to explain why it was happening, in terms I actually understood. My old wiring wasn't working well with the new wiring where we had done a renovation. He fixed the problem quickly once he determined what it was.\nHe also helped install my new Ring Doorbell. If I ever have any issues occur again in the future, I will definitely be calling for Kyle again! Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Boyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6fHOQFp3iZm9nXsarMrM2K8Jci6ZvaneJ8QRX1H2urgbh5Agg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was able to schedule an appointment over the phone and Kyle came within the next few days. He was able to inspect and repair the switch within half an hour. He was honest and genuinely educational. They're open about prices and don't try to blind side you. Will definitely be contacting them in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marissa Mangan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyaB7jMfDcPIz3BYQg9AXruh8X4D4qVHF-D65QnJ7KmxSiMTt-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle from Beacon Hill Electric arrived on time and did an excellent job adding an outlet in my garage. He also left the area spotless afterward. Highly recommend him! So impressed with his punctuality and attention to cleanliness!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corin R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuKqG6exGymeMSvEYpFJdbECyfdnGASuQ9UvuGpwazRA1x1OGk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Beacon Hill Electric to handle the wiring for our DIY bathroom remodel project. The electrician installed two new vanity lights, a bathroom fan, and added two new receptacles exactly where we wanted them with minimal drywall damage. We're thoroughly impressed and grateful for their excellent work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shan IL","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWkkDRf8Ki7VVHHCOHHkbMEQUH1qNn_4cwTwWxEgG9bz8cJx4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had outlet work done by another company. Unbeknownst to me, they butchered the job and left me at risk of a house fire.\n\nOnly found out because Beacon Plumbing was out at my house checking on a leaking pipe.\n\nBrett \u0026 Sam came over right away, assessed the hazardous outlets (there were 6), quoted me for the fix, and went to work on the repairs. They were kind, took the time to help me understand the problem, and why I was at risk, and went the extra step to check other outlets around the area to ensure they were safely installed.\n\nCan’t thank them enough for the quick, easy, and quality service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Schloredt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLX9_5kJO6pJ9lkBE856zHHqCv3XFMUA_tL1FWm2qt0ft2M6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a set of lights that were not working and reached out to Beacon Hill Electric. Kyle quickly determined the problem as a broken breaker and had the lights back in working order promptly. As a project manager for a construction company, I have worked with many subcontractors and found the service from Beacon Hill Electric kind, quick and professional.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dash (Unchikun)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9w90p3y2j8iRKzRPlP6kF8Am9YaYOgIgitcSn7AbmJHz3DjUo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired beacon hill electric to install 2 new lights. Kyle came out and did a good job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFFQyK8zhHcerU5KYKZb2EdAqtA3pjlG-Oh7AyqWJYDs6Aww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle replaced several outlets and added several new circuits into a difficult-to-access part of my home. I was very happy with his work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
