c68/public/requests/4592411/new?rwg_token=AFd1xnGXn5y601kGVGJpB9fp-gkpR4JBba2fw3XZP3wdaaVMUyAGBMkYQlNqhC6R4BZFvaEy5k_y_M82MpjVsJUUaK1HmwFWXS9ujpMNw4OdvDAElnQBWcE%3D","source":"getjobber.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"106349116594341621835","name":"Reddie Electric LLC (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106349116594341621835"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"1206 Mill Creek Blvd","city":"Mill Creek","postal_code":"98012","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as Latino-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Paul Goris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiUnrcORNtGSEgXGS0Z0zRfIY3hDCPaRZKFjuGgqIf4FNPxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Early Sat morning we experienced sparks and smoldering from our in wall heater. We contacted multiple vendors but only one responded, REddie Electric LLC. Eddie provided insite into what steps to take to keep us safe until his arrival and greatly decreased our anxiety. Eddie arrived exactly at the time he committed to (1100) and quickly diagnosed the issue in terms easily understood. He arrived fully prepared to resolve the problem and also addressed and resolved other existing problems we hadn't mentioned prior. I was impressed with his professionalism, courtesy, focused listening, and competency. I highly recommend him and his business for both the speed they resolved our issues and the professionalism he displayed during his execution. Plus, he is a very nice personally with significant soft skills. I was impressed enough to contract for other long delayed needs in my home due to my trust in him. I offer my highest level of recommendation.\n\nPaul Goris 1/28/2026","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCqc0SdPI9k0BEZ4FeKh95lLiyldpnQIDTTq_El8GayJ1x1wGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a serious problem with our main circuit breaker, and our power was completely out for over five hours. It was already after 5 PM, extremely cold, and the situation was honestly scary for our family.\n\nWe contacted Reddie Electric LLC, and Eddie came out to help us. From the start, he was professional, calm, and extremely knowledgeable. He quickly diagnosed the issue and worked efficiently to restore our power.\n\nThanks to Eddie, our heat came back on, and he truly saved our family from the cold. We are so grateful for his help during such a stressful time. He went above and beyond, and you can tell he genuinely cares about the people he helps.\n\nEddie is the best electrician, and I would highly recommend him to anyone who needs reliable and compassionate service. Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Berry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0K0JAsHKx3WrrB6XjQmUDKcVKUjAlXrBTCmyoPowLro0C1l_j=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best electrician.  He was recommended by another contractor which is always a good sign.  Eddie showed up exactly when he said he would.  He was quick, clean, and polite.  As he was leaving he asked me if there was anything else he could help with and i mentioned i might have him come back in the future to replace a car charger that had never worked correctly.  He took a look at it and quickly fixed faulty wiring that two electricians from another large electrical company had installed wrong. I am already walking around my house wondering what other things i would ideally like to have in my house that i can have Eddie come out and replace or add.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tianheng Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRe3IvZz5k1oQreBKWsGEgm3EGRRSdZODegrIo3pb90U5XUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eddie handled some rewiring and added a new outlet, and the experience was excellent from start to finish. He’s professional, efficient, and takes the time to explain everything clearly and patiently. The quality of his work is outstanding, everything was done perfectly with great attention to detail. Highly recommend Eddie if you need a skilled and reliable electrician.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mihir Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU92QbW57wbxC0XYCHXfSVmY3L1ZUv4Aj1wjbNW1o8XN_Dyew4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eddie and his team were fantastic to work with. They arrived on time, completed all the electrical work efficiently, and communicated clearly every step of the way. They made sure we understood what was being done and answered all of our questions. I highly recommend Reddie Electric and will definitely be using them again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandy Barnum Davidson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsE3yRrwcaRgr_d5pUBgEe71saPd38lzkM08LGkAWTt1z5SUfLjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used ready electric several times. They are always very polite, considerate, do a great job and a reasonably priced. They're very good at letting you know what they can do in a certain time period and then following up to schedule any further work if you happen to request that while they are there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jae Yoo (fkkcloud)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5Le2OQEPagdaBWIeAgx3XkiTem23shfdTNaRebqLMEJfQoz7U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eddie installed a Tesla wall charger in our garage, and we couldn’t be happier with the entire experience. From the very beginning, he was super easy to communicate with, always quick to respond, and made sure we fully understood the process. He was incredibly supportive throughout, patiently walking us through the options and finding the best and most cost-effective way to solve the problem.\n\nOn the day of installation, he showed up right on time, worked efficiently, and made sure everything was done neatly and safely. He clearly takes pride in his work and cares about delivering the best results for his customers. It’s rare to find someone this reliable, professional, and friendly, and we highly recommend Eddie to anyone who needs EV charger installation or electrical work done right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicholas Newton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNMStmZWrLNUMvCl8geLmrCorluQGeUDiCRFdKIIZAVdTiBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"At 1030pm on a weeknight our microwave turned stopped working. I tried to check the breaker but the second I touched it, the breaker box started buzzing like a game show buzzer. We called Reddie Electric and Eddie himself picked up right away and was in route immediately to help us. It turned out the issue was much larger than a bad breaker. The breaker was overloaded and included an outlet poorly wired with an open neutral putting extra wear and tear on the system. Even though it was super late, Eddie took his time and kept asking questions as to what led to the breaker going out. He was patient, kind, and a joy to have in our home at such crazy hours in the night. At 230 in the morning we parted ways with confidence we were safe. The panel was an old GE model and we had plans to upgrade our panel later in the year but I decided now was the time, so we had Eddie upgrade to a Square D panel. Again he and his partner Dustin redid our panel and did a great job too! I cannot recommend Reddie Electric highly enough.  Eddie and company are there for you when you need help.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
