3TZKEta_Oy2IuJGaVsS4G4hRZflqnchEH5ifhr5F2p37qNOIa-mxdfDLU4VgCFxlEXobo3OtAM6-feFZNnFhRIRQ58FFK05FSJb7=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0v-34YFOh_f-VHRyiUCPlogwBq_YuVU_2YnCM-MF4U93Lq0UgPAL2Q6EBJHijokHyzpUi6fb3z2RzUnek9dFgxTwmFY47EBgHKx9vMzJRk7P7kF52r19CbD-gj-rG1AajO92FS58i33bLb=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-25"},{"Name":"Michael Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVI-vOcb-7N2LGQ5dHA8AfWJzkslXOedCfknDYPd_BmZsavgHd4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I want to take a moment to share how exceptional our experience was this week with Kemly Electric. Kemly came to our condo to replace our electrical panel when we discovered issues with our original panel from the 1980's, and they were outstanding from start to finish. They explained exactly what was happening and why it was an issue, and the day of the service, they even finished their work early! Plus, the fee for their services was very reasonable for the work performed.\n\nThank you again, Kemly team! I have already shared your name and contact information with several of my friends and colleagues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jxj alt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuoaFP_kqRiXHKiEITA6MJoT-CtDBbch2T3gIjEwE5b2fm2u4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Kemly by another electrician. The office responded quickly but didn't harass me with multiple callbacks like some of the other places I got a quote from. I appreciated their simple pricing structure, compared to other places that wouldn't give me a number or had lots of fees and add-ons. Jonathan the electrician was great, clean and respectful and handled pets well. He fixed my problem quickly and actually helped me with a couple other small issues around the house while he was here. Would hire again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sahar Banijamali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPHLYIAXEP8sUW0_uIyDbWlUvwpPCNkCcGbmh1VLotGNeubgW1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience troubleshooting some fans and installing some lighting in the dormer.  Johnathan was the best, such a kind and nice human.  He was efficient, respectful, a great communicator and very fairly priced.  We'd love to have him do electrical work for us again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kara Gorman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3kgXT8lyhi_iLv2RPaLdC3OUbB7lOcDiEDr__SQCG88h3_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used Kemly 3 times now and been very happy with the service each time.  We've had Mike out twice now for smaller issues and he is fantastic.  Explains the issue and solution options very clearly and works with us to decide what makes the most sense for our situation.  Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia Frederick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXFNIbsyPzvor54mxqJTJoQZmv8nX82uGEF0sPps2-4e5dpmmH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kemley was incredibly responsive, professional, and friendly. They came to our house right away and fixed our outlet issue very quickly. They took the time to explain everything clearly, and they were so kind throughout the entire visit. We really appreciated the great service and would recommend them to anyone who needs electrical help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Renaud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkSBFSrrXbLmPTScHBVhzYCN0YT3Q_40ivNT8DKEyoQSFMAjs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Kemly! My thermostat went out on one of the coldest weekends and I was fortunate enough to get a same day appointment. The tech was friendly and efficient and explained to me what was going on so I knew what to look for if problems popped up again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D E Fenton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHCW8z43HJvxeLlKFW-QeSNXzotpaHY0kvsMqL_F7ddxsNDA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've used Kemly for all of our electrical needs since 2003. From remodeling my first condo kitchen to gutting my second condo to remodeling our newest home, they did it all. Knowledgeable people to work with, reasonable solutions to the surprises one finds in a mid-century modern house previously owned by a DIY-er and affordable rates.\nMost recently, in preparing our condo for sale, we had to switch out all the electrical outlets, switches \u0026 covers to white from ivory (outdated!). We also had to change out the diningroom fixture. Braiden did the did the whole job in one day: 27 outlets, 4 HDMI outlets, 4 GFI outlets, 5 dimmer switches, 2 fans, 6 regular switches and replacing ceiling-mounted swag fixture. Impressive. And he cleaned up after the work, as well.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
