l work in the future.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3LB7EyjS4PRke7ylT2SOChO4l5pw5IJPeBSWtImH_fe6JDbjR_MlX-omjwmG9T2GXKXevhxuAJV3Zg7E5k6sjGnZkOJoUBhtxV5mWNsOHauXcI3w1WsboDUNbtIX0M5N8ExuD0pg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VNUImtGLdlbdvC5wCDA-ug6HXCpeHJELaHuRfezqY86LYHIILK7eM4c4gZxazRgtSt8RTsfRYOKVfJRu0QjdxHzT5Tpm7K08bl4UstIe2DbmEIaVHk9DgDH2q4fjypIO4jcQ=k-no"],"When":"2022-3-31"},{"Name":"Tim Bosh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkLwJWOZs_qTZg-luLSZc7po67PO4G3uar_M1fVBNu51JPZA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spoke with the owner of the company to discuss my project ideas. He was knowledgeable and provided quotes that were fair. They were able to get two people out within a few days to complete a 6 hour job. We have no complaints, the technicians arrived on time, worked quickly, and cleaned up after themselves.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0KQJDCO4dW0v8Gd6KpfYEP1VcPtkLN7rmWXl7ftUMiAIKfqCSw57ird1ykXws9v7OOod2wE4gYiftIrXMI4NVDEGqX87xG0z8i0voFZHolxON4sgtyO3ddv2AXJR8tt4ypjiZdhg=k-no"],"When":"2023-3-2"},{"Name":"Jasmine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5i4TvTMRvby6lahPm_TlKefhmG8ogiq5RLOIBpqUA8Vszeg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finding a reliable electrician was proving to be super difficult until I got in contact with Eugene. Everything was so smooth, gave me a quote on the spot and was able to get my work scheduled the same week. Mike was my technician and he was fabulous!! Highly recommend and have already referred this company to my friends. I got a 240v outlet installed and they also fixed a few of my smart plugs/ random house electrical work. Worked so clean and quick!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doug J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBxI-e8achNDoK63NdHpkRbMNb0qu5OsC_yXW1vt81igzM7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed to upgrade our outdated electrical panel. Eugene came out and did a great job with the upgrade. He explained everything fully and truly cares about the quality of his work. It was clear to me he was very knowledgable about his craft.\nHis prices are very competitive. This solved our issues with tripping breakers and we haven't had a single problem since the upgrade. I would highly recommend Reign City Electric for your electrical needs.\nDoug J.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Abner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLblgj9CdKt56Dgcr-h1WqRukS6uI4KoVqRuinMBDW7NjvcJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reign City Electric was awesome and I will definitely use them again for future electrical work. Eugene is very knowledgeable and responsive with communications. The electrician that came out was on time, assess the situation and quickly installed a new circuit breaker. I was very pleased with the work and service provided.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Rang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6fsuiFpjjMzlPgCJOQ2LwehssVWRfU5NTnWXkMM5l_0wTWjDn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Reign City to install a light fixture in an awkward spot in my house (in the middle of a hallway with a 13-ft ceiling). They were very responsive and came over quickly to install the fixture. They did a great job and I couldn't be happier. I would definitely recommend using Reign City if you need an electrician in the Seattle area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Parsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnFMWno9zw4GmevJqDxm6Brk81oeoWPzmrCbkUpMzauyU8XRHM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They did a great job. Fast, affordable and efficient. I'm happy with my new fixture. Totally worth having someone help who knew what they were doing in a tall hard to reach area.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Hg3yYnY-BrHgnm0fhPErwIw7IV_eK