g":5,"Description":"Live Wire always provides top notch customer service, quick responses, reliable and honest work. Everything from their booking process to arrival \u0026 job completion is seamless. They do a great job of keeping you up to date on all expected costs and estimates so nothing comes as a surprise. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1mc4SWZqOF37BUtKeWsLc-3KiurXNes8q9QqZ2REoWiFo-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly professional and thoughtful help. They were immediately responsive and made my project work. Very transparent pricing and excellent customer service from people who know what they are doing. The owner Brian came out to work on one issue and then took the time to troubleshoot all the other problems I was having and questions I had. I signed up for the membership they offer because I want them to come and do additional work. They made the schedule work for me and the unique demands of my project. I’ve worked with other electricians and they are my new go to. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
