ions, did a great job, and left the area clean when he was finished.\n\nWhen I called to set up the appointment, the office staff was kind and easy to work with as well. Overall, it was a smooth, easy experience. We would definitely recommend them and use them again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elliot Lobo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSc3to_JMwJxM0cKWEDzMpBA8ZDDblfVvah5V-7tjZiRUclw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience with Roger installing my Tesla EV charger. He was incredibly easy to work with and made scheduling simple and stress-free. He arrived on time, was exceptionally professional, and clearly very knowledgeable.\n\nBefore starting the job, Roger walked me through every step which I really appreciated. He went above and beyond by cleaning the electrical panel and patching up the drywall holes, leaving the space better than he found it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Lisondra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcoy3FyyeEciMQNUbKzJQdaY6HDf1kk9-g7xm7EtdqJGlcCMW2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Galaxy Electric did a great job installing my outdoor electric outlet s.  They were on time and cleaned up after the work was done.  Great work today!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0IileuerNYhRUHXNXuqtYLRuUkGNdZwluliZ6ADGWLlxY-hDGYeQTBCNea0Mk42jeLgD3voUX6VXMjOVtgGxgQCCnSamuJeMRvvLc4era4ObeLTmE_VDDpBmJbUFOTEMgKTMojfd09dZg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0wQNnTTKHP18sUgzkUgz0hRwmqSNgKEXlWGPMXGRsJOxBThjfdzr3cF14ov_s_4-KTmT_eoorFW9xDs1tw9RaMOBf79hdhLCCQypOIqTNdRLGXXXRlTzXPPUeza3dJNon8LMSlLwJNaTU0=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-19"},{"Name":"Vincent Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlMHfUwkgbTuARR1MpKXZJRdaKiwrjN1YZKhWG5FxIBC0y30s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Galaxy Electric \u0026 Solar did an excellent job fixing our lights and installing