was their efficiency — they worked quickly without cutting corners, cleaned up everything afterward, and made sure the system was tested and running exactly as I wanted before leaving.\n\nIf you’re looking for a contractor who’s responsive, meticulous, and delivers high-quality results without delay, Gold Mountain Contracting is the team to call. They turned my vision into reality in just one day.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2cUCcowlPg4atmKR20c4lmicp5jVsg9sneVrxVZhZ39pyolHJJtlJgjBS27B-srsXejAqBF899xau6P-UvHL6LrCVZok_H4Jvr5Bp2LtTPOT1DaBIT__XIJOcaaujyH9C3yRJrrv9JXaig=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-8"},{"Name":"Douglas Vojir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUA7jjI2NwoiNfOp11LyUgG9yNkwJdqXo2emOBTqGysiXRt5WY9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an issue in my kitchen, and they called and left a message for me to do some simple checks on my own first, which was appreciated and which I did), but they had to come over anyways. Cade and Tucker got right to work, checking the nearby outlets, the junction box in the attic and the circuit breaker downstairs. They found the issue behind the pot cabinet, and fixed it right up. It was a great experience and I can highly recommend them 👍","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Kt4tdKPvrcF_EVq6xsaAaCSSjdeGts06dEkXUZaEJLO8Z5V48Xe2U6zwBwhJjbKa2bNrn1uZNEpHYMvv0LV2JdHGTr9ygiaBAg-1pjVE0KidOb3IiQAXK3UQbWSjHW8GDKU19S9GCBt0=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-15"},{"Name":"d b","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQvFZbqvfF26l_W2vUlLiHJBmrGZ8Ej1EsmfN9q-J7kZ073rDk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don't quite know how to make this review really capture the experience I had with Gold Mountain. This crew was amazing. Everything about the way they work impressed us. From the expertise in assessing our project scope, the detailed questions and expert opinions to refine it, the confidence they showed in carrying the project to successful completion - these are all basics, and with them, they deftly navigate those dynamics at a level of ultra professionalism.\n\nBut they're magic. They're wizards and carry all the charisma you could ever dream of in working together. We felt like we were part of their team. Somehow, they made their work seem like a blast to deliver. So much insight, humor and positivity was shown.\n\nOur project had some really big challenges that involved coordination across 7 teams. Gold Mountain by far showed the strongest front, and managed to help us carefully step through some of the minefields that arise when so many teams are doing work on the same program. The result of their involvement gave us huge confidence in working with them again, whenever the need would arise. Always reasonable, always offering clear direction and assistance in making heavy decisions. Always communicative, on time, and faithful to follow up on anything needing further attention.\n\nJust look at the results of their work. They did all the exterior electrical work on our remodel. Can't wait for an excuse to use them again. Tucker, Cade, Jordan - you are all superstars amongst the trade.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Ge1G1AeYtk1ccSgn_-zx5qETfncR0mLAu6An_BNomX0vEWYhv9Liv59XgwtDtYk8crOdP5dDfN7esU27m9k836gybt1N0RbwB90QflGbfVAqsq91IjmlV_eRKcOJ9e_gVssLPSr1qqJU=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-2"},{"Name":"Anna E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6EPPPqCakbZl_bZTuL5XsYRDAACZwnUOQoz50VZO9Hr6_gA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Second time working with them, this time on new lighting fixture installation in two different rooms. Electrician Cade was very helpful in helping me find the right fixtures for the spaces and my use cases, everyone involved was super friendly and willing to answer my questions, and the work was done quickly and efficiently with minimal inconvenience.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2W