530-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=Sl9-jymKCmPVVTyhiFvc4A\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=253.1932\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"116209978029990228686","name":"Seattle Electricians Today (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116209978029990228686"},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Admiral","street":"4701 SW Admiral Wy #230","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98116","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"L H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKm3GS7EkualmcePssfwuJFsGN10rhmYhqdD7zztElEWkMjkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeff and Ben rewired our 1924 home, ridding it of all knob and tube and we couldn’t be happier. They took great care in minimizing damage to our walls, significantly less than what we expected and what we were told by other contractors.\n\nWe looked for an electrician who not only had extensive experience with wiring older homes, but also a history of positive reviews; Seattle Today Electricians met both of these criteria.\n\nEach day they were great in cleaning up work areas, as well as answering all our questions and keeping us informed if they found any areas Jeff felt needed more attention; he is very knowledgeable.\n\nI appreciated the care they took in being aware of out two indoor cats as they entered and exited our home while working, never once did a cat escape.\n\nAndrea is also great in scheduling and facilitating a smooth project. During this time I had many medical appointments; she made sure our inspection accommodated my appointments.\n\nWe felt very comfortable with them, there were times we left them alone in our home with no concerns.\n\nOur inspection passed with no issues. Jeff will be our go to electrician moving forward for all our electrical needs; we highly recommend him and Ben.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Joy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcaE-hWait5T98SpUsPQAhSOEf1xcoV1Vz9outaDtcj48qSq62=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a general contractor in West Seatttle and I use Electrician's Today for all my residential work.  Jeff's vast knowledge electricity, and of all facets of construction, makes him invaluable on my projects.  Jeff's team is top notch and will undoubtedly make you happy you called!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MkspH8XbCWEVQrubfsZvCvU4bCot_1vG4G668DgCkO8iQWZ6z5xK_cbl4u-PszYw667ryPDGvtmg9DEXF6UkvLCgVe1X1chm1eBOpBehhiaDhtAIDN0PFBUG2Fgv5wp1u9Z5I=k-no"],"When":"2017-3-8"},{"Name":"Alex Sundell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfeLBh5TDfPSGjLwJ5fl9DhTgI9YSkCvo5-IM8Gn352543xKb2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeff was incredibly helpful in identifying an electrical issue with my home.  When the problem became an emergency and hazard, Jeff was on site within the hour to resolve it and restore power.  Andrea was also very communicative and helpful in coordinating getting Jeff on site and communicating with the power company.  I would highly recommend Seattle Electricians Today for any residential electrical needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cherie Singer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQgpVd3UGxV2Yw49nXcQMO3be7Q08hxovHEiY3upgoe2t9Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't say enough about what great work Jeff did on my 1925 home. I needed a complete electrical overhaul from the old knob \u0026 tube wiring, as well as new outlets in all rooms, not to mention other upgrades.  Jeff and his team were communicative, quick, clean, and non-disruptive to my life during the process.  I had many, many other bids, and was told I'd have numerous, huge holes in my walls. Jeff made no holes, except of course around a few outlet covers - minimal.  He came in at a lower price and did what I know is a much better job than the rest. Five Stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roadto Freedom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJahHUACijJGFJl_MTVYZw9d8YI6q1Vr5-79qCMC7rTPk6Ejw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We used Electricians Today to update wiring on a home we purchased that had unsafe 1970's wiring. Jeff is ultra competent and knowledgeable. It was especially wonderful that he arrived and did the work exactly in the timeline and price range promised.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJBcDJh0TFyT_Kw_igOKcDkK_Z6OqwOvY65T3aOhhuoWb6n7WR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeff is awesome. He’s installed several lights for us and recently has come by to check on some minor things that we (stupidly) couldn’t solve ourselves (and was kind enough to not charge us). The scheduler Andrea is great too. We love having a local and dependable electrician available anytime something in our older house comes up. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Cockrum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJW8G1kx5imBMwVTK2l7FiTrMFp3KskYW_ZjvqX_Yvced2YYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed a service replacement done on a 1950s house that had the original wiring.  Our electrician (Jeff) was on time, experienced, and professional during the installation and answered all my questions.  The city inspector was happy with his work and said to tell him he did a good job.  Would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Richardson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEUeMDDtehBYBFdDv9bLHNJbU7p-NrMlaDCORkPy1DetGHme-EeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow - showed up same day even though booked for the rest of the month, they worked me in for an outdoor outlet 