","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1Ws-KH-RnSUxWHIr9BxO1lGg1-ytLxkEibb0RBL_IQcPdKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So Schneider electric is no longer here those people moved out but this house is great 5 stars would recommend. 👍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xitang Zhao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLRKjO8Ou0dOg9q-SlD24o-6rGUGw7xdwPOdxZGOuIpeZhgsM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of our circuit breaker flipped in the cold winter day right before Christmas. We were struggling to fix it for several hours with no luck, so we gave Schneider Electric a call. Josef had deep domain expertise and asked us several great questions to troubleshoot. He was able to help us fix it remotely and not charging a fee - best Christmas gift anyone in our shoe could have received. I don’t normally write review but can’t help leaving one for their kind helps. Merry Christmas!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bill Savage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8uaQ1YPBq5RZDq5sCiH44w8Bs2fz5C86NeklZsHNFZBolv-yH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Josef and Jamey are outstanding at what they do.  I really appreciate their professionalism, creative problem-solving, and willingness to make their customers happy.  I had an electrical scenario that was challenging, and they handled it quickly, perfectly, and creatively.  I couldn't be happier with the results of their work.  I highly recommend Schneider Electric, and I would absolutely call them again.  Five Stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paula Berry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9NUOIR61qo7SEtV91mJFf0dJXTmG7MJld8a0wKchxvSGC7rY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used Schneider Electric for multiple issues in my downtown Seattle condo over the past seven years. I have had nothing but great experiences and service, and highly recommend them. In addition they have been the preferred ‘go to’ electrical company for the building manager in this 174 unit high rise building whenever electrical work has been needed, even on an emergency basis. They are knowledgeable, professional, and a pleasure to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bill Leder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeoh6CAWWIjeKZhg16WV5GK92DYGLaQGqDN50epftUL_FbGagJLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Schneider Electric in Edmonds won the bid to install a meter base and 200 AMP panel in my detached garage.  Josef Schneider was a good listener and provided expert advice, and estimated the job accurately.  Jamey did the actual work and was a great source of information and very thorough and professional.  The job was completed and Inspector approved on-time and on-budget.  I highly recommend Schneider Electric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Don Kaufman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVo-iYN1e-hNF1MFlhe9wPO8FrG-J5ZuUsVNJcNhdvsqDN8YTn_vA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was during the snowpocalype of 2019 when we had an electrical surge hit our house.  We had a bunch of issues, but Schneider sent someone quickly, in 18 inches of snow, to fix our issues.  Will use for any future non-emergency needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Scheir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhGpgwghoQgybdE8UpoKLEKr5t9bLgc-zFUTPZse0GuZlGiTGtLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible customer services. Rude over the phone. Would not recommend this business.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
